Fast rising Kogi born artiste, Ali Zainab Nielsen aka Alizee, has reportedly been shot dead alongside her 4-year-old daughter, Petra Nielsen. She was murdered on the 5th of April by her Italian husband, Peter Nielsen, at their home in Banana Island, Lagos. Before her untimely death, Alizee was promoting her new song ‘Alhaji Musa’ and was also billed to perform at Harrysong’s ‘Kingmaker Concert’ at the Warri Stadium on April 29th. The circumstances leading to her death still remains unknown but their bodies have been deposited at a mortuary by the police. The husband is currently being held at the Ikoyi police station.

